----------Passenger Books a ride-----------
Actors: Passenger
participant: MobileApp, ridecontroller, bookingservice,rideRepository, bookingrepository, notificationService,Driver 


Passenger>>MobileApp; select ride and request Booking 
MobileApp>>RideController: requestBooking(rideId, passengerID,seats)
BookingService>>rideRepostiory; findById(rideID)
RideRepostiory>>BookingService: ride 

---Ride has available seats-------
BookingService>>BookingRepostiory: Save(new Booking)
BookingRepostiory-->>BookingService: Booking 
BookingService>>notificationService: notifyDriver(Booking created )
notificationService->>Driver: booking request notification 
BookingService-->>RideController: BookingPending (booking)
RideController-->MobileAPP: showBooking Pending 

else; "no seaets available" 
 BookingService-->>RideController: error("No seats available")
        RideController-->>MobileApp: Show error message
    end
